name: Kings of the Porcelain Stars
description: Hailing from the Osmerian Sea, the Kings of the Porcelain Stars are known for their belief and allegiance to the semi-sentient forest, Amoria Now working as diviners - those who navigate the dreams of others in order to heal mental afflictions, they look towards the future with a glint in their eye. Their future is bright. The only question: what comes next?
